scenario_id | scenario_name | use_climate_K | use_human_K | use_hunting | climate_file                    | human_file                          | hunting_file                 | K_formula                                        | description
M1          | baseline      | 0             | 0           | 0           | NA                              | NA                                  | NA                           | K_t = K5200                                      | 基线情景；不施加气候变化、人类耕地压力和狩猎死亡
M2          | climate       | 1             | 0           | 0           | input/climate_K_factor.tsv      | NA                                  | NA                           | K_t = K5200 * climate_K_factor                  | 气候情景；仅适宜栖息地变化影响环境承载量
M3          | human         | 0             | 1           | 1           | NA                              | input/human_K_factor_{level}.tsv    | input/hunting_{level}.tsv    | K_t = K5200 * human_K_factor                    | 人类活动情景；耕地面积影响K，聚落数量影响狩猎死亡
M4          | combined      | 1             | 1           | 1           | input/climate_K_factor.tsv      | input/human_K_factor_{level}.tsv    | input/hunting_{level}.tsv    | K_t = K5200 * climate_K_factor * human_K_factor | 联合情景；同时考虑气候变化、耕地扩张和狩猎死亡